'''顺反组'''（{{lang-en|cistrome}}）指的是“全基因组尺度下[[反式作用|反式作用]]因子的[[顺式作用|顺式作用]]靶点的集合，也可以说是在体情况下[[转录因子结合位点|转录因子结合位点]]或[[组蛋白|组蛋白]]修饰在全基因组上的位置”<ref name="pmid21859476">{{cite journal | author = Liu T, Ortiz JA, Taing L, Meyer CA, Lee B, Zhang Y, Shin H, Wong SS, Ma J, Lei Y, Pape UJ, Poidinger M, Chen Y, Yeung K, Brown M, Turpaz Y, Liu XS | title = Cistrome: an integrative platform for transcriptional regulation studies | journal = Genome Biol. | volume = 12 | issue = 8 | pages = R83 | year = 2011 | pmid = 21859476 | pmc = 3245621 | doi = 10.1186/gb-2011-12-8-r83 | url = }}</ref>。“顺反组”这一术语是<u>cistr</u>on（顺反子）和gen<u>ome</u>（基因组）的[[混成詞|混成詞]]，最初由[[达纳-法伯癌症研究所|达纳-法伯癌症研究所]]和[[哈佛医学院|哈佛医学院]]的研究者命名<ref name="urlcistrome / FrontPage">{{cite web | url = http://cistrome.pbworks.com/w/page/10521472/FrontPage | title = cistrome / FrontPage | publisher = PBWiki, Inc. | work = | accessdate = }}</ref>。

